ComicInfo.Summary: One world. 63 million psychics. 63 million stories. "NIGHTINGALE," Part Two? In the wake of Cristina's dramatic escape, Hanley and the CIA calculate the cost. Hanley and his team endeavor to track Cristina down, but with a psychotic empath assassin on the loose, not even the CIA's best are safe! When Cristina and Hanley face off, who will survive?
